  "agentGuidance": "Pass --control-field <value> (values: OpenUrl, WaitTabComplete, ActivateTab, CloseTab, GetTabInfo, RunScript, PickElement, GetElementInfo, UpdateElement, TriggerEvent, Wait, SetBrowser, BackgroundScript, BackgroundCommand) to filter inputs/outputs. Each controlField.selection[] entry includes visibleInputKeys and visibleOutputKeys for that mode.",
